{"tid":1480093,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致生活喺香港既大陸人：","createTime":"2019-08-17T07:10:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T07:44:50.000Z","uid":185736,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"db9f0c4386c0060af0f2c3d8fd7e6e9e068a48ee","tid":1480093,"uid":185736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"想問你，點解會選擇香港？<br />\n香港有咩吸引你？<br />\n喺大陸讀讀下幼稚園，走落黎香港讀書。<br />\n為咩？<br />\n你落黎搶我地啲資源，<br />\n床位、醫療、學位、工作、公屋、生果金...<br />\n唔係香港咁多福利，你會落黎？<br />\n<br />\n咁你落到黎，慶幸成為香港人<br />\n揸住香港身分證，但你走去玩，<br />\n坐視不理，你好唔好意思呀？<br />\n咁你唔好同人講你喺香港人啦。<br />\n<br />\n香港依家搞成咁，你都有份。<br />\n聽日維園有大遊行，<br />\n可唔可以幫手出一分力，一齊行。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">8.18 需要你。<br />\n3點 &middot; 維園見 </span>"},{"pid":"de1d9962317f28366894fc7a93a0019b8c0a9b45","tid":1480093,"uid":185736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:11:03.000Z","msg":"歡迎分享比你地喺大陸落黎既朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a8443405d3296ed1daa2a238249de32acf5277","tid":1480093,"uid":185736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:11:41.000Z","msg":"比佢地睇下 當初落黎香港做乜"},{"pid":"e1177c76005ae1704bd9e4e2fdc5b60fd9dd02b2","tid":1480093,"uid":185736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:12:28.000Z","msg":"唔好再喺到repost啲新聞<br />\n就當關心左香港"},{"pid":"5388f3b64d7f1d4a2b09d9f6a081f7904d9434a6","tid":1480093,"uid":185736,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:12:54.000Z","msg":"出黎一齊行，唔該你。"},{"pid":"3c12a0f0869178bb6fdedc95f06c5e273e192296","tid":1480093,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:12:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"98e13ec3146a3a20e032ade52e9ab586836e2d73","tid":1480093,"uid":185736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:13:42.000Z","msg":"喺香港生活左十幾二十年<br />\n你自己問下自己攞左幾多野<br />\n但你為香港付出左啲咩？"},{"pid":"6ddd81349b0e4e634a6e1e223bfcc374cc43723d",